were pretty slow. Real slow and forklift-like 
guys. But good maneuverability in the mud. They

36:05.485 --> 36:06.767
deployed those. One of my sergeants, if that had 
got into us, you see, our guns wouldn't penetrate

36:07.688 --> 36:19.225
their tanks. We had to The only way we'd penetrate 
