36:40.015 --> 36:50.292
hell out of them and just keep fighting them and 
maneuver again and try to get on their flanks, you

36:40.015 --> 36:50.292
know, and hit them in the flank where they're soft 
instead of taking them head on. It was hard to

36:50.713 --> 36:59.467
maneuver and they were maneuvering to beat hell in 
