38:47.039 --> 38:54.308
you shooting over you— Over me, absolutely. I 
never got a chance to engage them. It wouldn't have

38:56.771 --> 39:00.495
done any good anyway because they'd have knocked 
me out.

39:02.990 --> 39:04.753
Soils. It killed us. Soils. Day after day after day 
after day of the utilization of massive

39:07.839 --> 39:16.213
firepower. And that's been a key to my whole 
tactical philosophy. of used firepower, you make

39:22.312 --> 39:25.837
that by hand. Don't use soldiers. They're 
important. They're made by God, grace of God. So

39:31.204 --> 39:33.848
why use something important? People are 
important. Use some cheap materialistic thing.

