41:14.513 --> 41:19.380
that I had received during the war. So the Germans 
were waiting for you then? The Germans were

41:24.107 --> 41:32.539
waiting for us, and they occupied the high ground 
on the other side of the Ruhr River.

41:33.060 --> 41:41.112
They had the observation on me, and I had to go take 
that objective anyway. How many casualties did

41:41.547 --> 41:43.310
you take? I had

41:45.152 --> 41:55.728
four more, about five more tanks hit from enemy 
artillery. Before you could wipe out their

41:57.951 --> 41:59.733
artillery? Yeah, before we could get our 
artillery in range to hit them.

